OL,3,CAlanis Morissette returns to Lytham
OL,4,CFestival
OL,6,FAlanis Morissette is set to headline
OL,7,FLytham Festival, a year after her
OL,8,Foriginal performance was cancelled due
OL,9,Fto adverse weather conditions.
OL,11,FShe'll play to 25,000 fans on on
OL,12,FThursday 2 July, in one of only five
OL,13,FUK performances next summer.
OL,15,FThe seven-time GRAMMY award winner the
OL,16,Ffinal headliner revealed for the
OL,17,FLancashire festival, completing the
OL,18,Fline-up.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
