OL,3,CAlanis Morissette returns to Lytham
OL,4,CFestival
OL,6,FAlanis said: "Lytham we are going to
OL,7,Fmake this happen! I am so happy to be
OL,8,Fable to announce I can come back to
OL,9,Fyou in 2026 so let's make this a huge
OL,10,Fnight to remember."
OL,12,FAlanis Morissette's career stretches
OL,13,Fover 30 years. Her debut album Jagged
OL,14,FLittle Pill was turned into a Broadway
OL,15,Fmusical in 2019, winning two Tony
OL,16,Fawards.
OL,18,FShe is known for hits like Ironic, You
OL,19,FOughta Know, Hand in My Pocket and
OL,20,FThank U.
OL,26,@rD@SO]
