OL,3,CAlanis Morissette returns to Lytham
OL,4,CFestival
OL,6,FLytham Festival co-founder Peter
OL,7,FTaylor said: "We are thrilled to be
OL,8,Fable to welcome Alanis Morissette
OL,9,Fback. She is a cultural phenomenon and
OL,10,Fjudging by the reaction to her shows
OL,11,Fin the UK this summer there is little
OL,12,Fdoubt her arrival in Lytham will be a
OL,13,Fmassive night."
OL,15,FOther headliners for the 15th
OL,16,Fanniversary of Lytham Festival include
OL,17,Fmulti-award winning Michael Buble,
OL,18,Fsuperstar rapper Pitbull, and the
OL,19,Ficonic duo Pet Shop Boys.
OL,26,@oD@NOUyD@arr
