OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1783064871
OL,3,CAlanis Morissette returns to Lytham
OL,4,CFestival
OL,6,FMr Taylor said: "Alanis completes our
OL,7,Fline-up of headliners for 2026. It's a
OL,8,Fvery special year for us celebrating
OL,9,Fthe 15th Lytham Festival and to have
OL,10,Fsuch international icons on the bill
OL,11,Fwill make for a very memorable five
OL,12,Fdays."
OL,14,FAlanis will be joined on Thursday 2nd
OL,15,FJuly by Skunk Anansie.
OL,17,FThe band formed in London in 1994 are
OL,18,Fknown for their powerful fusion of
OL,19,Fhard rock, punk, and funk influences.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
